---
// Static CTA section — monthly meetup call-to-action
---

<section class="py-16 border-t border-gray-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Join Our Monthly Meetups</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <strong>Open to makers & 3D printing enthusiasts of all age, skill, and interest levels.</strong><br />
      Join our Facebook Group to get notified about upcoming events and connect with the community.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/makerdeck"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#1877F2] hover:bg-[#166fe5] text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 text-xl shadow-lg transition transform hover:scale-105"
    >
      <i class="fab fa-facebook mr-2"></i> Join Facebook Group
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
